    "body": "@mpetrunic  I modified `packages/lodestar/src/chain/factory/block/index.ts` like this:\r\n```\r\nlet start = Date.now();\r\n  const state = stateTransition(config, currentState, block, false, false);\r\n  console.log('@@@ stateTransition took ', Date.now() - start);\r\n  start = Date.now();\r\n\r\n  block.stateRoot = hashTreeRoot(\r\n    state,\r\n    config.types.BeaconState\r\n  );\r\n  console.log('@@@ hashTreeRoot took ', Date.now() - start);\r\n```\r\nand run blockAssembly.test.ts unit test again. The result is\r\n```\r\n@@@ stateTransition took  0\r\n@@@ hashTreeRoot took  821\r\n@@@ total time of test  898\r\n```\r\nMost of the time is for hashTreeRoot(), state transition takes very small time.\r\nIt proves that stateTransition stub works well and there is a performance issue of hashTreeRoot.",
